    <descgrp type="admin">
      <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
        <p>
The record group is an amalgam of records from different donors. The bulk of the records came from Fred Hoffman (donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">10117</num>) in 2008; one township record book was donated by Louis Doll (donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">1338</num>) in 1985; and the school records were donated by Edna R. Faulkner (donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">3024</num>) in 1953.</p>
      </acqinfo>
      <accruals encodinganalog="584">
        <p>
No further additions to the records are expected.
</p>
      </accruals>
      <accessrestrict encodinganalog="506">
