    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <p>Sylvan Township is located in western Washtenaw County.  Chelsea is the largest city in the Township.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <p>The record group consists of township board records, 1834-1910, justice of the peace docket books, 1885-1925, assessment books, 1859-1886 (with some gaps), minutes of the board of school inspectors, 1866-1894, and records of School District Number 7 records, 1837-1910.</p>
    </scopecontent>
